---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseHead title="Contact - Master Azerbaijani" />

<Header />

<main class="page-container about-page">
  <h1>Contact Us</h1>

  <p
    style="
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto 25px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    "
  >
    Hi there! I’m Shahla from Master Azerbaijani. I’d love to hear from you. Whether you have suggestions,
    questions, or just want to share your story, don’t hesitate to reach out.
  </p>

  <p
    style="
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    "
  >
    Email us directly at:
  </p>

  <p class="contact" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">
    <a href="mailto:contact@masterazerbaijani.com">contact@masterazerbaijani.com</a>
  </p>

  <p
    style="
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    "
  >
    Feel free to ask about lessons, suggest new features, or share how you and your family
    are learning Azerbaijani. I aim to respond within 24 hours. Your feedback helps make
    Master Azerbaijani better for everyone!
  </p>
</main>

<Footer />
